comment:
* A set of constants that can relate to time or time zone detector status. * *
    *
  • Detector status - the status of the overall detector.
    • *
  • Detection algorithm status - the status of an algorithm that a detector can use. * Each detector is expected to have one or more known algorithms to detect its chosen property, * e.g. for time zone devices can have a "location" detection algorithm, where the device's * location is used to detect the time zone.
    • *
* * @hide

variables.name: DETECTOR_STATUS_UNKNOWN
variables.comment:
* The detector status is unknown. Expected only for use as a placeholder before the actual
     * status is known.

variables.name: DETECTOR_STATUS_NOT_SUPPORTED
variables.comment: The detector is not supported on this device.

variables.name: DETECTOR_STATUS_NOT_RUNNING
variables.comment: The detector is supported but is not running.

variables.name: DETECTOR_STATUS_RUNNING
variables.comment: The detector is supported and is running.

variables.name: DETECTION_ALGORITHM_STATUS_UNKNOWN
variables.comment:
* The detection algorithm status is unknown. Expected only for use as a placeholder before the
     * actual status is known.

variables.name: DETECTION_ALGORITHM_STATUS_NOT_SUPPORTED
variables.comment: The detection algorithm is not supported on this device.

variables.name: DETECTION_ALGORITHM_STATUS_NOT_RUNNING
variables.comment: The detection algorithm supported but is not running.

variables.name: DETECTION_ALGORITHM_STATUS_RUNNING
variables.comment: The detection algorithm supported and is running.

methods.name: public static int requireValidDetectorStatus(@DetectorStatus int detectorStatus)
methods.comment:
* Validates the supplied value is one of the known {@code DETECTOR_STATUS_} constants and
     * returns it if it is valid. {@link #DETECTOR_STATUS_UNKNOWN} is considered valid.
     *
     * @throws IllegalArgumentException if the value is not recognized

methods.name: public static String detectorStatusToString(@DetectorStatus int detectorStatus)

     * @throws IllegalArgumentException if the value is not recognized

methods.comment:
* Returns {@code DETECTOR_STATUS_} constant value from a string. See also
